OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1776719465
OL,3,CCrossbow fired at police and sword
OL,4,Cbrandished during stand-off in Kilkeel
OL,6,FA man has been arrested on suspicion
OL,7,Fof attempted murder after a crossbow
OL,8,Fwas fired at police and a sword
OL,9,Fbrandished in Co Down.
OL,11,FThe 40-year-old was detained following
OL,12,Fthe stand-off in Kilkeel which lasted
OL,13,Ffor several hours on Sunday.
OL,15,FOfficers discharged plastic baton
OL,16,Frounds and a Taser during the incident.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/10
