PN,44602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1776719465
OL,3,CCrossbow fired at police and sword
OL,4,Cbrandished during stand-off in Kilkeel
OL,6,FPolice were called to the Moorfield
OL,7,FCourt area at around 9pm after
OL,8,Fconcerned members of the public
OL,9,Freported a man in a balaclava armed
OL,10,Fwith a crossbow was in the street
OL,11,Fthreatening residents.
OL,13,FA PSNI spokesperson said: "Upon police
OL,14,Farrival the suspect had retreated to a
OL,15,Fnearby house and a prolonged stand-off
OL,16,Fensued.
OL,26,@uD@[OU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1776719465
OL,3,CCrossbow fired at police and sword
OL,4,Cbrandished during stand-off in Kilkeel
OL,6,F"Throughout a four-hour period both
OL,7,Flocal police and specialist armed
OL,8,Fresponse crews were subject to
OL,9,Fsustained attack from within the
OL,10,Fproperty, including being threatened
OL,11,Fwith a large sword and targeted with
OL,12,Fcrossbow bolts which narrowly missed
OL,13,Fresponding officers.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1776719465
OL,3,CCrossbow fired at police and sword
OL,4,Cbrandished during stand-off in Kilkeel
OL,6,F"The use of attenuating energy
OL,7,Fprojectiles (AEPs) and a conducted
OL,8,Fenergy device (CED) were authorised
OL,9,Fduring the police operation and were
OL,10,Fsubsequently deployed to prevent the
OL,11,Fman from harming himself or anyone
OL,12,Felse, and to enable police to safely
OL,13,Fremove him from the house."
OL,15,FThe suspect was detained and placed in
OL,16,Fpolice custody.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/10
