OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1776719465
OL,3,CCrossbow fired at police and sword
OL,4,Cbrandished during stand-off in Kilkeel
OL,6,FDistrict Commander Superintendent
OL,7,FLynne Corbett said: "The officers who
OL,8,Fresponded to this incident, both local
OL,9,Funiform crews and specialist
OL,10,Fresources, should be commended for the
OL,11,Fbravery and professionalism shown in
OL,12,Fwhat must have been a frightening
OL,13,Fsituation.
OL,15,F"The ability to hold your nerve,
OL,16,Fremain calm and prioritise the safety
OL,17,Fof not only the public but also the
OL,18,Fsuspect, in the face of a continuous
OL,19,Fpotentially life-threatening attack,
OL,20,Fis something that should not be
OL,21,Funderestimated.
OL,26,@oD@UOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1776719465
OL,3,CCrossbow fired at police and sword
OL,4,Cbrandished during stand-off in Kilkeel
OL,6,F"The arrested man received appropriate
OL,7,Fmedical review following the incident
OL,8,Fand will now be questioned on
OL,9,Fsuspicion of a number of extremely
OL,10,Fserious offences including attempted
OL,11,Fmurder, making threats to kill and
OL,12,Fpossession of an offensive weapon."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
