OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1776719465
OL,3,CCrossbow fired at police and sword
OL,4,Cbrandished during stand-off in Kilkeel
OL,6,FShe added: "I would also like to
OL,7,Fexpress my thanks to local residents
OL,8,Ffor the co-operation shown whilst we
OL,9,Fworked to bring the situation to a
OL,10,Fsafe conclusion, and I am appealing to
OL,11,Fanyone in the local area with
OL,12,Finformation that could assist the
OL,13,Fpolice investigation to please get in
OL,14,Ftouch with us."
OL,16,FThe senior officer made an appeal for
OL,17,Fanyone who had footage of the incident
OL,18,Fto contact police.
OL,26,@nD@LOUvD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1776719465
OL,3,CCrossbow fired at police and sword
OL,4,Cbrandished during stand-off in Kilkeel
OL,6,FSouth Down DUP MLA Diane Forsythe said
OL,7,Fit was a "horrific and deeply
OL,8,Ffrightening incident for all those
OL,9,Fliving nearby".
OL,11,FShe said: "I am extremely grateful
OL,12,Fthat no-one was physically harmed, but
OL,13,Fit will undoubtedly have caused
OL,14,Fsignificant distress within the local
OL,15,Fcommunity.
OL,17,F"I have been in contact with
OL,18,Fconstituents who were impacted and
OL,19,Fhave made representations on their
OL,20,Fbehalf.
OL,26,@oD@JOUqD@NO]sD@KOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1776719465
OL,3,CCrossbow fired at police and sword
OL,4,Cbrandished during stand-off in Kilkeel
OL,6,F"People have the fundamental right to
OL,7,Ffeel safe and secure in their own
OL,8,Fhomes, and incidents like this are
OL,9,Funderstandably very unsettling.
OL,11,F"I commend the calm and responsible
OL,12,Fmanner in which local residents
OL,13,Fresponded, and I pay tribute to the
OL,14,FPSNI for their swift and professional
OL,15,Factions in containing what was a very
OL,16,Fserious situation.
OL,18,F"It is important now that the justice
OL,19,Fprocess is allowed to take its course,
OL,20,Fand that those affected are supported
OL,21,Fin the days ahead."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUzD@AOU}D@SO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/10
